    "an5.243:0.2": "25. Duccaritavagga ",
    "an5.243:0.3": "Paṭhamavacīduccaritasutta ",
    "an5.243:1.1": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, ādīnavā vacīduccarite …pe… ānisaṁsā vacīsucarite …pe…. ",
